caption.0: We're celebrating the red, white, and blue and wishing you a wonderful 4th of July weekend!
caption.1: Our new sticker suite is here! Visit our stories for a closer look and find them wherever you get your GIPHY stickers.
caption.2: My goal is to make sure every Guest feels cared for. There was this one Guest in particular that pulled into our drive-thru and started placing an order with me. She was struggling to describe what she wanted. I recognized that she was speaking half English, half Spanish, so I decided to respond in Spanish. She said she was relieved and thankful to meet a Team Member who was bilingual. - Stacey @cfahicksvilleGracias, Stacey, for the way you serve!
